OL,3,CTrain disruption after Birmingham New
OL,4,CStreet station evacuated due to fire
OL,6,FRail passengers are facing major
OL,7,Fdelays in and out of Birmingham New
OL,8,FStreet station after it was evacuated
OL,9,Fdue to a fire.
OL,11,FEmergency crews were called to the
OL,12,Fscene on Friday morning (10 July) and
OL,13,Fall train services were suspended.
OL,15,FAccording to Birmingham New Street the
OL,16,Fstation was evacuated whilst fire
OL,17,Fservices isolated a fault on board a
OL,18,Ftrain.
