OL,3,CTrain disruption after Birmingham New
OL,4,CStreet station evacuated due to fire
OL,6,FThe station has since reopened but
OL,7,Frail passengers are being warned of
OL,8,Fdelays of up to 60 minutes and some
OL,9,Fcancellations on CrossCountry and West
OL,10,FMidlands Railway between Birmingham
OL,11,FNew Street and Manchester Piccadilly,
OL,12,Fand between Birmingham New Street and
OL,13,FLiverpool Lime Street.
OL,15,FThere are also delays of up an hour on
OL,16,Fsome cancellations on Caledonian
OL,17,FSleeper and Avanti West Coast between
OL,18,FBirmingham New Street and Edinburgh
OL,19,FWaverley.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
