OL,3,CTrain disruption after Birmingham New
OL,4,CStreet station evacuated due to fire
OL,6,FOn social media, Birmingham New Street
OL,7,Fsaid: "The station has now reopened.
OL,8,FThere will be delays as services
OL,9,Freturn to normal. Check your journey
OL,10,Fand the latest travel information.
OL,12,F"Thank you for your patience."
